        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=Nat.cast_id#doc\">docs#Nat.cast_id</a> states that if you cast an natural integer <code>n</code> towards the natural integers you get the same. In your problem your integer is not cast towards <code>ℕ</code> but <code>ℝ</code> so it can't work. You can use <code>norm_cast</code>, it will get rid of the coercion.</p>",
